{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-mdx-frontmatter-type-mdx-frontmatter-slug-js-content-file-path-content-docs-pseudo-classes-additional-classes-mdx","path":"/docs/additional-classes/","result":{"data":{"mdx":{"id":"f98d4609-1220-5b4d-83e3-fc1a6f89304d","body":"\r\nimport { Paragraph } from \"../../../src/components/Mdx/textComponents\"\r\n\r\n# Overview of the Additional pseudo-classes\r\n\r\n#### Other Classes that respond to Pseudo States\r\n\r\nThe additional Classes that respond to pseudo states are\r\n\r\n- Font Size\r\n- Font Family\r\n- Font Weight\r\n- Text Decoration\r\n- Border and Outline Classes\r\n\r\nNot all of these can be transitioned, although maybe some can be faked - for example you can fake smooth font weight transtitions by getting creative with text shadow - (but that's kind of weird for a framework I think, but maybe a good opportunity to write some custom SCSS if you want it). But some of these can, I'll try to include transitions for the transitionable properties in the examples.\r\n\r\nOf course everything on this page can be customized for your own theme in the `_variables.scss` and see the (Customize)[/customize/] section of the docs for more details!\r\n\r\nLet's start with Font Size!\r\n\r\n## Font Size\r\n\r\nFont size is supported by pseudo classes, although it's a bit of a special use case. I thought it was useful enough to include, although be careful going too wild because they might conflict with any responsive font size styles. Going wild with font size and pseudo classes would likely be best handeled by writing some custom SCSS for most cases I can imagine, although utility classes probably still come in handy if you just need some styles that aren't gonna be too eclectic:\r\n\r\n| Class Example | CSS rule             | Example                                                    |\r\n| :------------ | :------------------- | :--------------------------------------------------------- |\r\n| text-xs       | font-size: 0.375rem; | <Paragraph className=\" text-xs\" text=\"Font Size XS\" />     |\r\n| text-sm       | font-size: 0.625rem; | <Paragraph className=\" text-sm\" text=\"Font Size SM\" />     |\r\n| text-md       | font-size: 0.875rem; | <Paragraph className=\" text-md\" text=\"Font Size Med\" />    |\r\n| text-base     | font-size: 1rem;     | <Paragraph className=\" text-base\" text=\"Font Size Base\" /> |\r\n| text-lg       | font-size: 1.25rem;  | <Paragraph className=\" text-lg\" text=\"Font Size Large\" />  |\r\n| text-xl       | font-size: 1.5rem;   | <Paragraph className=\" text-xl\" text=\"Size XL\" />          |\r\n| text-2xl      | font-size: 2rem;     | <Paragraph className=\" text-2xl\" text=\"Size 2XL\" />        |\r\n| text-3xl      | font-size: 3rem;     | <Paragraph className=\" text-3xl\" text=\"3XL\" />             |\r\n| text-4xl      | font-size: 4rem;     | <Paragraph className=\" text-4xl\" text=\"4xL\" />             |\r\n| text-5xl      | font-size: 5rem;     | <Paragraph className=\" text-5xl\" text=\"5XL\" />             |\r\n\r\nPseudo Class Examples:\r\n\r\n<table className=\"w-3/4 mx-auto max-scr:w-full max-scr:mx-0 mt-lg mb-2xl mt-xl\">\r\n  <thead className=\"display-block pr-2xl letter-spacing-xl\">\r\n    <tr className=\"display-flex\">\r\n      <th className=\"display-flex font-large text-lg w-1/4 max-tab:w-1/5 \">\r\n        Example\r\n      </th>\r\n      <th className=\"display-flex justify-center font-large text-lg w-1/2 max-tab:w-9/20 \">\r\n        Html\r\n      </th>\r\n      <th className=\"display-flex justify-center font-large text-lg w-1/4 max-tab:w-1/5\">\r\n        Result\r\n      </th>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </thead>\r\n  <tbody className=\"display-block max-h-48 overflow-y-auto pr-lg\">\r\n    <tr className=\"display-flex py-sm border-dotted border-green-ltr bb-sm min-h-2\">\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/4 justify-center pr-lg max-tab:pr-md max-tab:w-1/5 sizing-border\">\r\n        Font Size with Hover\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/2 max-tab:w-9/20 max-tab:mr-sm  justify-center \">\r\n        ```html\r\n        <p\r\n          class=\"\r\n            text-lg \r\n            hover:text-xl\r\n            cursor-pointer\"\r\n        >\r\n          Hover Me\r\n        </p>\r\n        ```\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/4 max-tab:w-1/5 center text-lg\">\r\n        <Paragraph\r\n\t\t\t\t\tclassName=\"text-lg hover:text-xl cursor-pointer\"\r\n\t\t\t\t\ttext=\"Hover Me\"\r\n\t\t\t\t/>\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr className=\"display-flex py-sm border-dotted border-green-ltr bb-sm min-h-2\">\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/4 justify-center pr-lg max-tab:pr-md max-tab:w-1/5 sizing-border\">\r\n        Font Size with Active\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/2 max-tab:w-9/20 max-tab:mr-sm  justify-center \">\r\n        ```html\r\n        <p\r\n          class=\"\r\n            text-lg  \r\n            active:text-xl\r\n            cursor-pointer\"\r\n        >\r\n          Press me\r\n        </p>\r\n        ```\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/4 max-tab:w-1/5 center text-lg\">\r\n        <Paragraph\r\n\t\t\t\t\tclassName=\"text-lg active:text-xl cursor-pointer\"\r\n\t\t\t\t\ttext=\"Press Me\"\r\n\t\t\t\t/>\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr className=\"display-flex py-sm border-dotted border-green-ltr min-h-2\">\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/4 justify-center pr-lg max-tab:pr-md max-tab:w-1/5 sizing-border\">\r\n        Text Size with Focus\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/2 max-tab:w-9/20 max-tab:mr-sm  justify-center \">\r\n        ```html\r\n        <input\r\n          class=\"\r\n            text-lg \r\n            active:text-xl\r\n            border-sm\r\n            w-1/2\"\r\n          value=\"Focus Me\"\r\n        />\r\n        ```\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/4 max-tab:w-1/5 center text-lg\">\r\n        <input\r\n          className=\"\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\ttext-lg \r\n            focus:text-xl\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\tborder-sm\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\tw-3/5\"\r\n          value=\"Focus Me!\"\r\n        />\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n\r\n  </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n## Font Family\r\n\r\nFont family can also respond to Pseudo States. The framework comes with 3 default font families, probably one of the first things one would want to do when starting a project is change the fonts to their theme, which can be done in the `_variables.scss` file (see [Customize](/customize/) section). I purposefully choose a basic font that one would probably want to edit to drive this point home haha (although I it works good for this site!)\r\n\r\n| Class Example | CSS rule                                 | Example                                                    |\r\n| :------------ | :--------------------------------------- | :--------------------------------------------------------- |\r\n| font-default  | font-family: \"Lato\", sans-serif;         | <Paragraph className=\"font-default\" text=\"Font Default\" /> |\r\n| font-large    | font-family: \"Francois One\", sans-serif; | <Paragraph className=\"font-large\" text=\"Font Large\" />     |\r\n| font-header   | font-family: \"Bebas Neue\", sans-serif;   | <Paragraph className=\"font-header\" text=\"Font Header\" />   |\r\n\r\nPseudo Class Examples:\r\n\r\n<table className=\"w-3/4 mx-auto max-scr:w-full max-scr:mx-0 mt-lg mb-2xl mt-xl\">\r\n  <thead className=\"display-block pr-2xl letter-spacing-xl\">\r\n    <tr className=\"display-flex\">\r\n      <th className=\"display-flex font-large text-lg w-1/4 max-tab:w-1/5 \">\r\n        Example\r\n      </th>\r\n      <th className=\"display-flex justify-center font-large text-lg w-1/2 max-tab:w-9/20 \">\r\n        Html\r\n      </th>\r\n      <th className=\"display-flex justify-center font-large text-lg w-1/4 max-tab:w-1/5\">\r\n        Result\r\n      </th>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </thead>\r\n  <tbody className=\"display-block max-h-48 overflow-y-auto pr-lg\">\r\n    <tr className=\"display-flex py-sm border-dotted border-green-ltr bb-sm min-h-2\">\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/4 justify-center pr-lg max-tab:pr-md max-tab:w-1/5 sizing-border\">\r\n        Font Family with Hover\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/2 max-tab:w-9/20 max-tab:mr-sm  justify-center \">\r\n        ```html\r\n        <p\r\n          class=\"\r\n            hover:font-large\r\n            cursor-pointer\"\r\n        >\r\n          Hover Me\r\n        </p>\r\n        ```\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/4 max-tab:w-1/5 center text-lg\">\r\n        <Paragraph\r\n\t\t\t\t\tclassName=\"hover:font-large cursor-pointer\"\r\n\t\t\t\t\ttext=\"Hover Me\"\r\n\t\t\t\t/>\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr className=\"display-flex py-sm border-dotted border-green-ltr bb-sm min-h-2\">\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/4 justify-center pr-lg max-tab:pr-md max-tab:w-1/5 sizing-border\">\r\n        Font Family with Active\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/2 max-tab:w-9/20 max-tab:mr-sm  justify-center \">\r\n        ```html\r\n        <p\r\n          class=\"\r\n            active:font-header\r\n            cursor-pointer\"\r\n        >\r\n          Press me\r\n        </p>\r\n        ```\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/4 max-tab:w-1/5 center text-lg\">\r\n        <Paragraph\r\n\t\t\t\t\tclassName=\"active:font-header cursor-pointer\"\r\n\t\t\t\t\ttext=\"Press Me\"\r\n\t\t\t\t/>\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr className=\"display-flex py-sm border-dotted border-green-ltr min-h-2\">\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/4 justify-center pr-lg max-tab:pr-md max-tab:w-1/5 sizing-border\">\r\n        Font Family with Focus\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/2 max-tab:w-9/20 max-tab:mr-sm  justify-center \">\r\n        ```html\r\n        <input\r\n          class=\" \r\n            focus:font-large\r\n            border-sm\r\n            w-6/10\"\r\n          value=\"Focus Me!\"\r\n        />\r\n        ```\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td className=\"display-flex flex-col w-1/4 max-tab:w-1/5 center text-lg\">\r\n        <input\r\n          className=\" \r\n            focus:font-large\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\tborder-sm\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\tw-3/5\"\r\n          value=\"Focus Me!\"\r\n        />\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n\r\n  </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n## Font Weight\r\n\r\ntodo\r\n\r\n## Text Decoration\r\n\r\ntodo\r\n\r\n## Border Width and Style\r\n\r\ntodo\r\n\r\n## Outline Width and Style\r\n\r\ntodo\r\n","frontmatter":{"description":"An overview of Additional Classes","title":"Additional Classes","type":"docs","image":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"f98d4609-1220-5b4d-83e3-fc1a6f89304d","frontmatter__type":"docs","frontmatter__slug":"additional-classes","__params":{"frontmatter__type":"docs","frontmatter__slug":"additional-classes"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Additional Classes","tags":["pseudo-classes"],"type":"docs","category":"pseudo-classes","description":"An overview of Additional Classes","slug":"additional-classes","order":40,"anchorLinks":[{"title":"Font Size","link":"font-size"},{"title":"Font Family","link":"font-family"},{"title":"Font Weight","link":"font-weight"},{"title":"Text Decoration","link":"text-decoration"},{"title":"Border Width & Style","link":"border-width-and-style"},{"title":"Outline Width & Style","link":"outline-width-and-style"}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2241216091"],"slicesMap":{}}